data.description: Don't miss out on this beautiful home, sitting on an almost quarter acre property, with a fenced in yard! This home can also accommodate first floor living with a private entrance  to potential third bedroom and full bathroom, or another common living space. The back room off the first floor kitchen offers versatility for the new owner so the choice is yours! The current owner has added upgrades to the house including bathroom and kitchen updates, a deck expansion and more. This spacious yard, on a quiet street, will make this a house you will love to come home to! Make your appointment today!
